value.0: Baba Yaga is a cannibalistic witch who lives in a hut on the edge of the forest. The hut stands on chicken legs and will only lower itself after Baba Yaga said a certain rhyme. A picket fence surrounds the hut and she places the skulls of her victims on it. For transportation Baba Yaga uses a giant mortar which she drives at high speed across the forest floor by steering the pestle with her right hand and sweeping away all traces of her passage with a broom in her left hand.

Use this portal to port to the leader of your leveling party. 

Usage Rules:

* Once use per rest
* You are under level 40
* Party Leader under level 40
* Party Leader within 10 levels of you
* Party Leader not within 25 metres of a hostile creature

This is mainly to help people who are leveling, not people who are PK'ing. Please use it that way.
